{"tid":1568221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下次真係要冷靜啲","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:35.000Z","uid":80395,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"879dafe03a59ca229dbc464c1464ee35ae9557c2","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"我知冷氣軍師無資格講咩，但係我地二百萬人佢地唔敢出黎就係明知唔夠人多就會危險，就算搞都係等散咗，捕係元朗搞。<br />\n<br />\n第一件事，大家要對愛國份子有信心，每次都一定有唔少係為左錢，而我地既目標係要係佢派錢既時候去打氣助興，我地就係勝在人多，一知係邊就總有幾個係左近，搞得多久而久之就會少左人敢出。<br />\n<br />\n記住，收錢一刻，佢成身錢係最脆弱既時候。"},{"pid":"6fef44cf5da79680be87e70326d865fe24c19f61","tid":1568221,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"唔可以變中國內戰<br />\n有機會外國唔會再幫香港人<br />\n<br />\n私了不被發現除外"},{"pid":"1ececf2c20d7ff6825b2cea6809791ec38645bd3","tid":1568221,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"一齊唱今天我咪算囉，做乜咁衝動"},{"pid":"d52abbe4f514782241c951a161d1bf771500c520","tid":1568221,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"應該打既時候唔打<br />\n成堆狗去左淘大保護黑社會，有晒記者拍片，你地就想出去打<br />\n200流浮山刀手果日又唔見有人出黎守？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲打啲落單既就得<br />\n唔需要硬碰硬<br />\n要10個打1個，唔係1個打10個<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各區接藍絲放工，保家衛邨，民間自衛</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">低調</span>先盡興"},{"pid":"cb03e171ce6be7e15dc62ffd5131c79fc72e695a","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"1168654b3c5560c53feef35bd77959432dc8b11f","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"d287c56e3125a4c9b14333bedc68d783f5fd794f","tid":1568221,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTARdd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTARdd6.jpg&h=4bdd572d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09df6cb929d836ded89674dfc6760b1bdf22e3f","tid":1568221,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"今日試完硬碰硬，不如下次試下冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />救下大家一齊試<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">提提大家：\n\n兄弟爬山各自努力 \n\n唱歌 勇武 和理非 覺得啱就去做\n\n見到有分化post可以善用不推文</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5def7f841ecbf13747199d1671cbdb59ff73d71a","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"fcdb5b2097c7e58ce12afea4b062a65314011581","tid":1568221,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"撇除假和理非，真正和理派，可以考慮吓上多啲前線，尤其是武力升級成本已經低咗唔少<br />\n<br />\n［升級彈藥］淘大有休班警執法，代表我哋可以做啲乜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2b3943f27952db44e2059edf21f37348c36314a","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"954c6f8353a45a4060cad63fd6820a8324947017","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"fe582212fad3257e93046ede66275b0edacd2ff1","tid":1568221,"uid":80395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"自推，不割蓆"},{"pid":"50af82812c2066ca87639c84169d8f97e1300fde","tid":1568221,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲都識見到人多就縮啦<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺唱榮光集會嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺組團修牆嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺大遊行嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為佢哋知自己吹雞唔夠人會俾人打返轉頭啊</span></span><br />\n連藍絲都識敵進我退,去淘大嗰班就唔識,明知冇PLAN好一定唔撚夠人都照衝,重蠢過藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使再問遊行有警察係咪唔去<br />\n屌你咩每次遊行宣傳咗幾耐?有PLAN定有事前計劃會夠人囉,夠人咪去囉<br />\n朝早宣佈下晝有遊行,然後現場有幾百隻狗等你,你都唔撚去啦<br />\nbe water唔代表啲water識瞬間移動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日去淘大嗰班&quot;手足&quot;,同825嗰隻藍衫的士佬一樣咁戇鳩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkUVtU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkUVtU.gif&h=8cdf3b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係以為藍絲企定定俾你打,以為自己可以一打十咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}